                | enter deatils and submit
            form(action='', method='POST')
            p Run Query:
            input(type='text', name='firstname', placeholder='tag list')
            br
            input(type='text', name='lastname', placeholder='id')
            br
            input(type='number', name='uuid', placeholder='name')
            br
            input(type='number', name='age', placeholder='model')
            br
            input(type='text', name='country', placeholder='producer')
            br
            +button("success", "/users", "small", "Add Product")
            if error
